{"article_id":"IAQmUGO7hv7ISKbz","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"`` The president will work with Congress","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to get this done , ''","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"the White House says","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"The House Speaker says","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"his Plan B was n't voted on","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"because it did n't have `` sufficient support ''","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"A bill","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"to alter cuts","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"did narrowly pass the House ;","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"the White House says","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"it would veto","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"The fiscal cliff 's tax hikes and spending cuts are set to take effect in January","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"House Speaker John Boehner 's proposal","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"to avert the looming fiscal cliff 's automatic tax increases","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"failed to curry enough Republican support Thursday night ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"after which Congress left for the holiday with no clear end in sight in the high-stakes debate .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Boehner said earlier Thursday","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"that he was confident","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"that his so-called Plan B","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"-- which would extend tax cuts","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"that are set to expire at year 's end for most people","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"while allowing rates to increase to 1990s levels on income over $ 1 million --","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"would pass the House ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"and in the process put pressure on President Barack Obama and the Democratic-controlled Senate .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"But his gambit seemed in doubt later","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"as Republican leaders struggled to get most all their members to sign on","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"-- even enlisting senators like Sen . Rob Portman ,","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"to work the House floor --","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"knowing","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"the chamber 's Democrats oppose it .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Then , around 8 p.m. , House Majority Leader Eric Cantor announced","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that the measure would not go up for a vote","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"as planned .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"`` The House did not take up the tax measure today","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"because it did not have sufficient support from our members","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"to pass , ''","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"Boehner said in a statement .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"`` Now it is up to the president to work with Senator","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"( Harry )","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"Reid on legislation","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"to avert the fiscal cliff . ''","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Democratic leaders already had signaled","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"they oppose the so-called Plan B .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"After Thursday night 's unexpected reversal , Republican legislators walked past reporters through the halls of Congress ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"and most did not take questions .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"One","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"who did","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"-- Rep. Jeff Flake , an Arizonan","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"who will move to the Senate next month --","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"he was disappointed .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"Obama to Boehner :","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"'Take the deal '","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"MUST WATCH Obama to Boehner :","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"'Take the deal '","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"02:55","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Fiscal cliff worries charities","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"MUST WATCH Fiscal cliff worries charities","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"02:42","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"JUST WATCHED Boehner 's fiscal cliff Plan B","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"MUST WATCH Boehner 's fiscal cliff Plan B 02:34","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"`` It 's too bad ;","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"I 'd rather vote on it tonight , ''","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"said Flake ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"who said","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"he sides with Democrats","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"in backing the extension of tax cuts except for household income of more than $ 250,000 .","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"`` Get it done . ''","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"What this means next in the fiscal cliff talks is unclear .","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"From here , scenarios range from intensified and ultimately successful talks in the coming days or entrenchment","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"as the fiscal cliff becomes a reality next year ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"when a new Congress could enter negotiations with Obama .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"The Plan B was significant","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"because Republican leaders previously insisted","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"they would n't raise rates on anyone ,","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"while Obama called tax rates for those","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"earning more than $ 250,000","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"threshold","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"to return to 1990s levels","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"while extending tax cuts for everyone else .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Although the House did n't vote on Boehner 's tax measure ,","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"most Republicans did vote together earlier Thursday","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"as the House narrowly approved , 215-209 , a related measure","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"to alter automatic spending cuts","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"set to kick in next year under the fiscal cliff ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"replacing cuts to the military with reductions elsewhere .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"The Congressional Budget Office said","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"this would lead to $ 217.7 billion in cuts over the next decade , short of the $ 1.2 trillion in cuts","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"that would go into effect in January","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"if the fiscal cliff is n't averted .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"Moments after that vote , the White House issued a statement","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"indicating","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"it would veto this bill .","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"But that should be a moot point ,","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"since Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid has said","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"he wo n't bring it up for a vote .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"`` For weeks , the White House said","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"if I moved on rates ,","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"that they would make substantial concessions on spending cuts and entitlement reforms , ''","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"House Speaker John Boehner said","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"before his plan fell flat .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"`` I did my part .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"They 've done nothing . ''","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"While the Ohio congressman said","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"Obama seems `` unwilling to stand up to his own party on the big issues","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"that face our country , ''","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"Democrats say","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"Republican leaders are buckling to their conservative base","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"by backing off","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"as negotiations seemed to be nearing a deal .","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"White House spokesman Jay Carney called the GOP alternatives `` a major step backwards , ''","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"claiming","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"they 'd lead to extended tax cuts of $ 50,000 for millionaires .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"Reid slammed the two Republican measures","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"-- the one","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"that passed","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"and the one","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"that was n't brought up for a vote --","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"as `` pointless political stunts . ''","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"The war of words notwithstanding ,","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"Boehner , Carney and Senate Democratic leaders all said","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"they are ready to talk .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"Reid has said","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"the Senate","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"-- with many members attending a memorial service Friday and funeral in Hawaii on Sunday for Sen. Daniel Inouye --","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"will be back at work December 27 .","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"And after Thursday 's session , Cantor 's office said","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"legislative business was finished for the week","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"but the House could reconvene after Christmas","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"if needed .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"`` I remain hopeful , ''","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"Boehner said .","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"`` Our country has big challenges ,","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"and the president and I are going to have to work together","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"to solve those challenges . ''","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"JUST WATCHED Fiscal cliff and your taxes","depth":5},{"id":143,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":5},{"id":144,"text":"MUST WATCH Fiscal cliff and your taxes 03:26","depth":4},{"id":145,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":146,"text":"Sen. Murray cracks wise on Plan B bill","depth":6},{"id":147,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":148,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"Sen. Murray cracks wise on Plan B bill","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"00:52","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":152,"text":"Van Hollen :","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"GOP running away from table","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":155,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"Van Hollen :","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"GOP running away from table","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"03:50","depth":6},{"id":159,"text":"The possibility of a fiscal cliff","depth":7},{"id":160,"text":"-- which","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"economists warn","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"will hit the American economy hard --","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"was set in motion two years ago , as a way","depth":7},{"id":164,"text":"to force action on mounting government debt .","depth":7},{"id":165,"text":"Negotiations between top Congressional Republicans and Democrats resumed after Obama 's re-election last month","depth":6},{"id":166,"text":"as did the barbs from both sides .","depth":6},{"id":167,"text":"Polling has consistently shown","depth":7},{"id":168,"text":"most Americans back the president ,","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"who insists","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"wealthy Americans must pay more ,","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"rather than Boehner and his Republican colleagues ,","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"who have balked at tax rate hikes","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"and demanded spending cuts and entitlement program reforms .","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"A new CNN/ORC International survey","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"released Thursday","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"showed","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"that just over half of respondents believe","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"Republicans should give up more in any solution","depth":9},{"id":179,"text":"and consider the party 's policies too extreme .","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"The two sides seemingly had made progress","depth":7},{"id":181,"text":"on forging a $ 2 trillion deficit reduction deal","depth":8},{"id":182,"text":"that included new revenue","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"sought by Obama","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"and spending cuts and entitlement changes","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"desired by Boehner .","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"Senior administration officials said","depth":8},{"id":187,"text":"Obama and Boehner have not spoken since Monday ,","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"when the president made a counterproposal to a Republican offer over the weekend .","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"The president 's offer set $ 400,000 as the household income threshold for a tax rate increase .","depth":9},{"id":190,"text":"It also included a new formula for the consumer price index","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"applied to benefits for programs such as Social Security , Medicare and Medicaid","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"to protect against inflation , much to the chagrin of some liberals .","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"The new calculation ,","depth":13},{"id":194,"text":"called chained CPI ,","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"includes assumptions on consumer habits in response to rising prices ,","depth":13},{"id":196,"text":"such as seeking cheaper alternatives ,","depth":13},{"id":197,"text":"and would result in smaller benefit increases in future years .","depth":11},{"id":198,"text":"Statistics","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"supplied by opponents","depth":11},{"id":200,"text":"say","depth":10},{"id":201,"text":"the change would mean Social Security recipients would get $ 6,000 less in benefits over the first 15 years of chained CPI .","depth":9},{"id":202,"text":"Boehner essentially halted negotiations","depth":8},{"id":203,"text":"by introducing his Plan B on Tuesday .","depth":8},{"id":204,"text":"He described it as a fallback option","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"to prevent a sweeping tax increase","depth":9},{"id":206,"text":"when tax cuts","depth":10},{"id":207,"text":"dating to President George W. Bush 's administration","depth":10},{"id":208,"text":"expire in two weeks .","depth":9},{"id":209,"text":"The spending cut vote","depth":10},{"id":210,"text":"-- similar to one","depth":11},{"id":211,"text":"passed by the House last year","depth":12},{"id":212,"text":"that went nowhere in the Senate --","depth":12},{"id":213,"text":"was added to the docket later Thursday ,","depth":9},{"id":214,"text":"to appeal to conservative legislators","depth":9},{"id":215,"text":"upset about backing a tax increase","depth":10},{"id":216,"text":"without acting on spending","depth":11},{"id":217,"text":"and protecting the military budget .","depth":11},{"id":218,"text":"The House speaker 's reasoning was that the passage of Plan B and the spending bill would put the onus on Obama and Senate Democrats","depth":9},{"id":219,"text":"to accept them","depth":10},{"id":220,"text":"or offer a compromise .","depth":10},{"id":221,"text":"For now , the Obama administration wo n't have to weigh in on the tax part of that scenario .","depth":8},{"id":222,"text":"As to the House-approved spending cuts bill , White House spokeswoman Amy Brundage dismissed the GOP alternative as `` nothing more than a dangerous diversion ''","depth":6},{"id":223,"text":"for eliminating federal funding","depth":7},{"id":224,"text":"by negatively impacting millions of seniors , disabled individuals and poor and at-risk children .","depth":7},{"id":225,"text":"In a statement Thursday night , the White House did n't address Thursday 's House proceedings","depth":7},{"id":226,"text":"but referenced its top priority","depth":8},{"id":227,"text":"-- ensuring that 98 % of Americans do n't see their taxes rise in January .","depth":8},{"id":228,"text":"The statement expressed confidence","depth":8},{"id":229,"text":"that there will be deal on the fiscal cliff","depth":8},{"id":230,"text":"but with no explanation","depth":8},{"id":231,"text":"of how , when or what such an agreement would look like .","depth":8},{"id":232,"text":"`` The president will work with Congress","depth":8},{"id":233,"text":"to get this done ,","depth":8},{"id":234,"text":"and we are hopeful","depth":8},{"id":235,"text":"that we will be able to find a bipartisan solution quickly","depth":9},{"id":236,"text":"that protects the middle class and our economy , ''","depth":9},{"id":237,"text":"the White House said .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":475,"left":379,"right":474,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":379,"left":289,"right":378,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":244,"right":288,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":0,"right":243,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":243,"left":240,"right":242,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":239,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":239,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":241,"right":6,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":288,"left":253,"right":287,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":248,"right":252,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":246,"right":247,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":245,"right":9,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":245,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":247,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":252,"left":12,"right":251,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":251,"left":250,"right":16,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":249,"right":15,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":249,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":277,"right":286,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":260,"right":276,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":260,"left":17,"right":259,"relation